headline: 3 Reasons We’re Fans of DoorDash (DASH)
summary: Over the past six months, DoorDash has been a great trade, beating the S&P 500 by 13.3%. Its stock price has climbed to $254.99, representing a healthy 36.2% increase. This was partly due to its solid quarterly results, and the performance may have investors wondering how to approach the situation.
